{
  "name": "PictureFormat",
  "summary": "<p><strong>LinkFormat</strong> 对象只包含应用于链接 OLE 对象的属性和方法。<strong>OLEFormat</strong> 对象包含应用于 OLE 对象的属性和方法，无论这些对象是不是链接对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例设置了第一张工作表中第一个形状的亮度、对比度和颜色的变换，而且在该形状的底部裁剪了 18 磅。要使此示例执行，则第一个形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pictureFormat = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>\n    pictureFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.3</span>\n    pictureFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Contrast</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.7</span>\n    pictureFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> = msoPictureGrayscale\n    pictureFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">18</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在活动工作表的第二个形状图片的右侧裁剪 10 磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>包含应用于图片和 OLE 对象的属性和方法。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>){\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n       <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n        }\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n            <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n        }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Brightness",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定图片或 OLE 对象的亮度。该属性的值必须是 0.0（最暗）到 1.0（最亮）之间的数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置了第一张工作表中第一个形状的亮度。第一个形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.3</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状图片的亮度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Brightness</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "ColorType",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置应用于指定图片或 OLE 对象的颜色转换类型。<strong>MsoPictureColorType</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例通过 MsoPictureColorType 将第一张工作表上的第一个形状的颜色变换类型设置为灰度。第一个形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> = msoPictureGrayscale\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状图片的颜色转换类型是否为默认颜色转换。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ColorType</span> == msoPictureAutomatic)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoPictureColorType",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Contrast",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定图片或 OLE 对象的对比度。该属性的值必须是 0.0（最低对比度）到 1.0（最高对比度）的数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例设置了第一张工作表中第一个形状的对比度。第一个形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Contrast</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.8</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状图片的对比度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Contrast</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Crop",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Crop</strong>对象，该对象代表指定的 <strong>PictureFormat</strong> 对象的裁剪设置。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个图片要裁剪的高度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Crop</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureHeight</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一张工作表的第三个图片要裁剪的宽度设置为300磅。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Crop</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureWidth</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">300</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Crop",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "CropBottom",
      "summary": "<p>裁剪的计算是同图像的原始尺寸相关的。例如，如果插入一幅原始高度为 100 磅的图像，将其放大为 200 磅高，然后设置 <strong>CropBottom</strong> 属性为 50, 那么从图像的底部切除的将是 100 磅（而不是 50 磅）。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从指定图片或 OLE 对象的底部所裁剪下的磅数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在第一张工作表中第三个形状的底部裁剪了 20 磅。要使此示例执行，第三个形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropBottom</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*使用此示例可指定从选定的形状底部裁去的百分比，不管是否已调整了该形状的大小。为使此示例正常运行，选定的形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> percentToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;What percentage do you want to crop off the bottom of this picture?&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SelectAll</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapeToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShapeRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> duplicate = shapeToCrop.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Duplicate</span>()\n    duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ScaleHeight</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> origHeight = duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span>\n    duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cropPoints = origHeight * percentToCrop / <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    shapeToCrop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropBottom</span> = cropPoints\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "CropLeft",
      "summary": "<p>裁剪的计算是同图像的原始尺寸相关的。例如，如果插入一幅原始宽度为 100 磅的图像，将其放大为 200 磅宽，然后设置 <strong>CropLeft</strong> 属性为 50, 那么 100 磅（不是 50 磅）将从图像的左边被切除。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从指定图片或 OLE 对象的左边所裁剪下的磅数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在第一张工作表中第三个形状的左侧裁剪了 20 磅。要使此示例执行，第三个形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropLeft</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*使用此示例可指定从选定的形状左边裁去的百分比，不管是否已调整了该形状的大小。为使此示例正常运行，选定的形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> percentToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;What percentage do you want to crop off the left of this picture?&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SelectAll</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapeToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShapeRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> duplicate = shapeToCrop.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Duplicate</span>()\n    duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ScaleWidth</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> origWidth = duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Width</span>\n    duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cropPoints = origWidth * percentToCrop / <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    shapeToCrop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropLeft</span> = cropPoints\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "CropRight",
      "summary": "<p>裁剪的计算是同图像的原始尺寸相关的。例如，如果插入一幅原始宽度为 100 磅的图像，将其放大为 200 磅宽，然后设置 <strong>CropRight</strong> 属性为 50, 那么 100 磅（不是 50 磅）将从图像的右边被切除。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从指定图片或 OLE 对象的右边所裁剪下的磅数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在第一张工作表中第三个形状的右侧裁剪了 20 磅。要使此示例执行，第三个形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropRight</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*使用此���例可指定从选定的形状右侧裁去的百分比，不管是否已调整了该形状的大小。为使此示例正常运行，选定的形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> percentToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;What percentage do you want to crop off the right of this picture?&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SelectAll</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapeToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShapeRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> duplicate = shapeToCrop.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Duplicate</span>()\n    duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ScaleWidth</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> origWidth = duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Width</span>\n    duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cropPoints = origWidth * percentToCrop / <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    shapeToCrop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropRight</span> = cropPoints\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "CropTop",
      "summary": "<p>裁剪的计算是同图像的原始尺寸相关的。例如，如果插入一幅原始高度为 100 磅的图像，将其放大为 200 磅高，然后设置 <strong>CropTop</strong> 属性为 50, 那么 100 磅（不是 50 磅）将从图像的顶部被切除。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置从指定图片或 OLE 对象的顶部所裁剪下的磅数。<strong>Single</strong> 型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在第一张工作表中第三个形状的顶部裁剪了 20 磅。要使此示例执行，第三个形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropTop</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">20</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*使用此示例可指定从选定的形状顶部裁去的百分比，不管是否已调整了该形状的大小。为使此示例正常运行，选定的形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> percentToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">InputBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;What percentage do you want to crop off the top of this picture?&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SelectAll</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapeToCrop = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Selection</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ShapeRange</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> duplicate = shapeToCrop.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Duplicate</span>()\n    duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ScaleHeight</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> origHeight = duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Height</span>\n    duplicate.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Delete</span>()\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> cropPoints = origHeight * percentToCrop / <span class=\"hljs-number\">100</span>\n    shapeToCrop.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">CropTop</span> = cropPoints\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（float 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "TransparencyColor",
      "summary": "<p>如果想透过图片的透明部分始终看到图片后面的对象，必须将图片的 <strong>FillFormat</strong> 对象的 <strong>Visible</strong> 属性设为 <strong>False</strong>。如果图片有透明颜色且 <strong>FillFormat</strong> 对象的 <strong>Visible</strong> 属性被设为 <strong>True</strong>，则图片的填充可以透��透明颜色看到，但图片后面的对象将难以看到。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回或设置指定图片的透明色，以红-绿-蓝 (RGB) 值表示。必须将 <strong>TransparentBackground</strong>属性设置为 <strong>True</strong>，该属性才有效。仅应用于位图。<strong>Long</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本例将第一张工作表的第一个形状中带有 RGB 值的颜色设置为透明色，该颜色由 RGB(0, 0, 255) 函数返回。要使本示例执行，第一个形状必须是位图。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> blueScreen = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pictureFormat = shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>\n    pictureFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TransparentBackground</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    pictureFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TransparencyColor</span> = blueScreen\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示活动工作表的第二个形状图片的透明色是否为红色。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TransparentBackground</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TransparencyColor</span> == <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">255</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>))\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "TransparentBackground",
      "summary": "<div id=\"vstable\" style=\"font-family:&quot;white-space:normal;\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>MsoTriState 可以是下列 MsoTriState 常量之一。</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td>msoCTrue</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>msoFalse</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>msoTriStateMixed</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>msoTriStateToggle</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>msoTrue 图片中定义为透明颜色的部分显示为透明的。</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div><p>图片中定义为透明颜色的颜色部分显示为透明。</p>\n<p>如果想透过图片的透明部分始终看到图片后面的对象，必须将图片的 <strong>FillFormat</strong> 对象的 <strong>Visible</strong> 属性设为 <strong>False</strong>。如果图片有透明颜色且 <strong>FillFormat</strong> 对象的 <strong>Visible</strong>属性被设为 <strong>True</strong>，则图片的填充可以透过透明颜色看到，但图片后面的对象将难以看到。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>仅应用于位图。MsoTriState 类型，可读��。使用 <strong>TransparencyColor</strong>属性可设置透明颜色。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本例将第一张工作表的第一个形状中带有 RGB 值的颜色设置为透明色，该颜色由 RGB(0, 24, 240) 函数返回。要使本示例执行，第一个形状必须是位图。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> blueScreen = <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">RGB</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">24</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">240</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> pictureFormat = shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>\n    pictureFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TransparentBackground</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    pictureFormat.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TransparencyColor</span> = blueScreen\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Fill</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Visible</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第二个形状图片的背景设置为不透明。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">TransparentBackground</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "MsoTriState",
      "readonly": false
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "IncrementBrightness",
      "summary": "<p>调整图片亮度不能超出 <strong>Brightness</strong>属性的界限。例如，如果 <strong>Brightness</strong> 属性初始设为 0.9 并将 <em>Increment</em> 参数指定为 0.3，则结果亮度为 1.0（<strong>Brightness</strong> 属性的上限）而不是 1.2。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>按指定数值改变图片亮度。可以使用 <strong>Brightness</strong>属性设置图片的绝对亮度。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在第一张工作表上创建第一个形状的副本，然后移动并变暗该副本。要执行本示例，第一个形状必须是图片或 OLE 对象。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> worksheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = worksheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Shapes</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Duplicate</span>()\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IncrementBrightness</span>(-<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.2</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IncrementLeft</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IncrementTop</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">50</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第二个形状图片的亮度增加0.2。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IncrementBrightness</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.2</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Increment",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>指定图片的 Brightness 属性值的改变量。正值表示图片变亮，负值表示图片变暗。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    },
    {
      "name": "IncrementContrast",
      "summary": "<p>调整图片的对比度不能超出 <strong>Contrast</strong> 属性的上下限。例如，如果 <strong>Contrast</strong> 属性初始设为 0.9 并将 <em>Increment</em> 参数指定为 0.3，则结果对比度为 1.0（<strong>Contrast</strong> 属性的上限）而不是 1.2。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>按指定值改变图片的对比度。可以使用 <strong>Contrast</strong>属性设置图片的绝对对比度。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例增大第一张工作表上所有对比度未到最大值的图片的对比度。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shapes = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= shapes.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (shapes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoPicture || shapes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> == msoLinkedPicture) {\n            shapes.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IncrementContrast</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.1</span>)\n        }\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将活动工作表的第二个形状图片的对比度增加0.3。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> shape = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveSheet</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Shapes</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    shape.<span class=\"hljs-property\">PictureFormat</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">IncrementContrast</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">0.3</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Increment",
          "type": "number（float 精度）",
          "description": "<p>指定图片的 Contrast 属性值的改变量。正值表示对比度增大，负值表示对比度减小。</p>\n",
          "optional": false
        }
      ],
      "returns": "void"
    }
  ]
}